因為n_glass&gt;n_oil&gt;n_air<br />
光線會係air and oil boundary同oil and glass boundary各自reflect，而兩個reflection都係out of phase=180度phase difference<br />
所以最後兩條光線係冇phase difference，要令到佢地有phase difference (for destructive interference)就要令係oil嗰層個phase difference=(n+1/2)&lambda;，而光線一入一出所經嘅distance係2d，fianlly 2d=(n+1/2)&lambda;

